Here is the full run of Plop! from 1973 - 1976.  Many covers feature magnificently insane Basil Wolverton art.  Inside is Sergio Aragones and more.  All of the scans are nice quality and high enough resolution that they look good in cdisplay at 1360 wide.  I don't know who the scanners were but thank you, whoever you are.

The scans have been rarred and then changed to .cbr for the cdisplay crowd.  If you don't like cdisplay just change the .cbr back to .rar and then unrar it like any other rar file and you'll have all of the normal jpegs.

